      • setResult

        public Info.Builder setResult(DataValue result)
        Result of the operation. If an operation reports partial results before it completes, this property could be Set before the CommonInfo.getStatus() has the value Status.SUCCEEDED. The value could change as the operation progresses. This property was added in vSphere API 6.7 This property will be null if the operation does not return a result or if the result is not available at the current step of the operation.
        Parameters:
        result - New value for the property.
